---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro"
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro"
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Hedvig+Letters+Serif:opsz@12..24&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
	<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
	<title>Michael Pasimio Portfolio</title>

</head>

<body>		
	<Header />

	<div class = "hero">
		<div class="hero-textbox">
			<h3>Hi, I'm <br><strong>Michael</strong></h3>
			<p>I believe education is the cornerstone of a healthy, democratic society.</p>
			<div class="orange-line"></div>
			<em>Learning Designer, Educator, Innovator. <br>
			Based in Washington, DC</em>
		</div>
		
	</div>

	

<section class="mission">
	<h3>My Mission: Redefine Education</h3>

	<p>At its core, education is a meeting between human lives and public institutions.
	<br><br>
	This meeting is more than just a transaction; it's a lifelong experience with farreaching impacts.
	<br><br>
	My goal is to bring human relationships and community-building back to the core of the educational mission, designing educational systems that prioritize the health and success of not just individuals—but of entire communities.
	</p>
</section>

<section class="design-principles">
	<h3>My Design Principles</h3>
		<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-header">
				<img src="../../expand.png" class="expand-icon" style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" alt="Expand Icon">
				<img src="../../collapse.png" class="collapse-icon" style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" alt="Collapse Icon">
				<h4>radical inclusivity</h4>
			</div>
			<div class="principle-text">
				<p>ai text: Designing with empathy and a deep understanding of human needs, behaviors, and emotions.</p>
			</div>
	</div>
	<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-header">
				<img src="../../expand.png" class="expand-icon" style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" alt="Expand Icon">
				<img src="../../collapse.png" class="collapse-icon" style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" alt="Collapse Icon">
				<h4>system-thinking</h4>
			</div>
			<div class="principle-text">
				<p>ai text: Prioritizing the well-being and success of communities, fostering collaboration and collective growth.</p>
			</div>
	</div>
	<div class="principle">
			<div class="principle-header">
				<img src="../../expand.png" class="expand-icon" style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" alt="Expand Icon">
				<img src="../../collapse.png" class="collapse-icon" style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" alt="Collapse Icon">
				<h4>human-centered technology</h4>
			</div>
			<div class="principle-text">
				<p>ai text: Striving to create inclusive and accessible educational experiences that empower all learners.</p>
		</div>

</section>

	<Footer />

	<script src="../scripts/viewport-animations.js"></script>
	<script src="../scripts/collapsible-principles.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
